    "description": "Are you a skilled Senior Property Advisor looking for your next big career move? Indiabulls Real Estate in Bhubaneswar offers you the perfect platform to grow professionally and personally.\n\nAbout Indiabulls Real Estate:\nIndiabulls Real Estate is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Coordinate with legal teams for documentation and title verification\n• Build relationships with channel partners and brokers\n• Negotiate pricing, terms, and conditions on behalf of clients\n• Conduct site visits and property presentations for clients\n• Manage relationships with existing customers post-purchase\n• Liaise with banks and NBFCs for home loan assistance to customers\n• Coordinate with architects, contractors, and project teams\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBA from a recognized university\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Real Estate Law\n• Proficiency in Property Valuation\n• Proficiency in GIS Tools\n• Proficiency in RERA Compliance\n• Proficiency in MS Office\n• Proficiency in Market Research\n• Proficiency in Investment Analysis\n• Proficiency in Project Management\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Bhubaneswar, Odisha, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Indiabulls Real Estate!",
